<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>FirstBase</title>

    <!-- stylesheet -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-beta/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-/Y6pD6FV/Vv2HJnA6t+vslU6fwYXjCFtcEpHbNJ0lyAFsXTsjBbfaDjzALeQsN6M" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/icomoon.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/fb_favicon.ico">

    <!-- javascript -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.js"
            integrity="sha256-DZAnKJ/6XZ9si04Hgrsxu/8s717jcIzLy3oi35EouyE="
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript"
            src="https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.12.1/jquery-ui.js"
            integrity="sha256-T0Vest3yCU7pafRw9r+settMBX6JkKN06dqBnpQ8d30="
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://openapi.map.naver.com/openapi/v3/maps.js?clientId=N4U9SJyL2gHum0hz1FK4"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.11.0/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-b/U6ypiBEHpOf/4+1nzFpr53nxSS+GLCkfwBdFNTxtclqqenISfwAzpKaMNFNmj4" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-beta/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-h0AbiXch4ZDo7tp9hKZ4TsHbi047NrKGLO3SEJAg45jXxnGIfYzk4Si90RDIqNm1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</head>

<body>
<div id="loading"><div id="loader"></div></div>
<div id = "intro-area">
    <div id = "intro-text">
        새로운 장소를 갈 땐!
    </div>
    <a href="/index">
        <div id = "intro-logo">
            <img src="/img/layout/intro-2.png">
        </div>
    </a>
    <div id = "intro-text2">
        공간 단위 소셜 네트워크
    </div>
    <a href="/index">
        <div id = "intro-button">
            <button class="btn" type="button">
                시작하기
            </button>
        </div>
    </a>
</div>

<!-- Modal -->
<div id="introModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; padding: 10px; margin: 0;">

        <!-- Modal content-->
        <div class="modal-content" style="display: flex; flex: 0 1; justify-content: flex-start; align-items: center;">
            <div class="modal-header" style="align-self: flex-end; border: none;">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; flex: 1 1; justify-content: center; align-items: center; flex-flow: column wrap;">
                <div class="modalImage">
                    <img src="/img/layout/wrench.png" style="width: 100px; height: 100px;">
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; flex-flow: column wrap;">
                    <p>&nbsp;</p>
                    <p><h4>사이트 공사 중입니다</h4></p>
                    <p><h4>안드로이드 앱을 다운로드해주세요</h4></p>
                </div>
                <div class="modalImage" style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
                    <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.yogiwara.firstbase" style="width: 90%; height: auto;">
                        <img src="/img/layout/download.png" style="width: 100%; height: auto;">
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

<script>

    $(window).on('load', function () {
        $('#loading').remove();
        $("#introModal").modal();
    });

    $(document).on('click', '#intro-area', function(){
        $(location).attr('href', '/index');
    });

</script>
</body>
</html>